{
  "title": "Master Survey Build",
  "showProgressBar": "bottom",
  "pages": [
    {
      "name": "lndgRoot_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lndgRootPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>About this survey</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootText",
              "html": "<p>The goal of this survey is to gather information about how laryngeal paralysis (LarPar, LP) affects the lives of people and the animals they love. It's the first comprehensive online survey of its kind, and should take no more than ten minutes of your time.</p><p> We recommend taking the survey on a tablet, laptop, or desktop, but it works on phones, too. It just might take a few minutes longer because of the smaller screen .</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootCrossedOverHeading",
              "html": "<h3>About your LP companion<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootCrossedOverText",
              "html": "<p>We know how hard it is to lose one's beloved companion. If you're still grieving from the loss, maybe it's best to do the survey later when you've had time to heal. </p><p>If you'd like to continue now, now please tell us your LP companion's name and if your LP companion has crossed over the Rainbow Bridge. This will allow us to tailor the questions to your individual situation.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lndgRootCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "lndgRootCmpnName",
                  "title": "Please tell us your companion's name:",
                  "isRequired": true
                },
                {
                  "type": "imagepicker",
                  "name": "lndgRootCrossedOver",
                  "title": "Has your companion crossed over the Rainbow Bridge?",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "choices": [
                    {
                      "value": "deceased",
                      "imageLink": "./img-companions-rainbow.png",
                      "text": "Over the Rainbow Bridge"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "living",
                      "imageLink": "./img-companions.png",
                      "text": "Still here on Earth"
                    }
                  ],
                  "imageWidth": 120,
                  "imageHeight": 120,
                  "showLabel": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootMakeSelection",
              "html": "<p>Once you've made your selection, please choose 'Next' to begin the survey.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lvngRoot_page",
      "visibleIf": "{lndgRootCrossedOver} = 'living'",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngRootPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>Please tell us a little about yourself</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootText",
              "html": "<p>We believe you're more likely to help us if you know your data can't be used anywhere else. We're not asking for your last name, so we have no way to connect you with any of your private data. Click the links below to learn about how your privacy is protected and what we'll be doing with this survey information.</p><p>If more than one of your beloved companions have LP, you can take the survey for each of them. You can also update the survey responses for each animal, but only one set of results are saved for each Facebook account or email and each animal. Each time you take, it, existing results will be updated with the most recent ones.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngRootAboutSurveyPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "html",
                  "name": "lvngRootInfoPrivacy",
                  "html": "<div class='srvy-general-info'><img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='srvy-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;<a href='https://example.com' class='srvy-info-link' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>About your privacy</a></div>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "html",
                  "name": "lvngRootInfoYourData",
                  "html": "<div class='srvy-general-info'><img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='srvy-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;<a href='https://example.com' class='srvy-info-link' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>How will we be using your information?</a></div>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "title": "First, a little about you...",
              "name": "lvngRootAboutUserPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "title": "Your First Name:",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserName",
                  "isRequired": true
                },
                {
                  "type": "dropdown",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserCountry",
                  "title": "Country:",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "choices": [
                    "United States",
                    "United Kingdom",
                    "Germany",
                    "Canada",
                    "Australia/NZ",
                    "France",
                    "Spain",
                    "Portugal"
                  ],
                  "showOtherItem": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "livRootOptionalInfo",
              "title": "Age and Gender (optional)",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "html",
                  "name": "lvngRootDemographicInfo",
                  "title": "",
                  "html": "<p>We're asking for optional basic demographic information to help understand how different people manage the animals in their care. "
                },
                {
                  "type": "radiogroup",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserAge",
                  "title": "Age group:",
                  "isRequired": false,
                  "choices": [
                    "Under 20",
                    "20-34",
                    "35-49",
                    "50-64",
                    "Over 65"
                  ],
                  "hasOther": false
                },
                {
                  "type": "radiogroup",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserGender",
                  "title": "Gender:",
                  "isRequired": false,
                  "choices": [
                    "Woman",
                    "Man",
                    "Non-binary",
                    "Prefer not to say"
                  ],
                  "hasOther": true,
                  "otherText": "Prefer to self-describe"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "title": "Verification contact",
              "name": "lvngRootVerificationPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "html",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserText",
                  "html": "<p>We'll need to contact a random sample of participants for verification purposes. If you don't want to share your email, you can use your Facebook account name for verification via Facebook Messenger.</p><p>With your consent, we may also contact you to talk in more detail about your experience with LP.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "boolean",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserContactType",
                  "title": "Would you like to use email or Facebook Messenger for verification?",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "labelTrue": "Facebook",
                  "labelFalse": "Email"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "title": "Email address:",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserContactTypeEmail",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "visibleIf": "{lvngRootUserContactType} = false",
                  "inputType": "email"
                },
                {
                  "type": "html",
                  "name": "",
                  "title": "",
                  "visibleIf": "{lvngRootUserContactType} = true",
                  "html": "<div class='srvy-general-info'><img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='srvy-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;Please go to your Facebook account page and copy the URL, then paste it below. Example: https://facebook.com/my.user.name.</div>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "title": "Facebook account:",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserContactTypeFacebook",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "visibleIf": "{lvngRootUserContactType} = true",
                  "placeholder": "eg. https://www.facebook.com/my.profile.name",
                  "validators": [
                    {
                      "type": "regex",
                      "regex": "^(https?:\\/\\/)?(www\\.)?facebook\\.com\\/[a-zA-Z0-9.]{5,}$",
                      "text": "Please enter a valid Facebook profile URL, e.g., https://facebook.com/your.username"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "boolean",
                  "name": "lvngRootContactOK",
                  "title": "May we contact you to talk more about your LP experience?",
                  "isRequired": true
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lvngCmpn_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngCmpnPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngCmpnAboutCompHeading",
              "html": "<h3>Tell us about your LarPar companion!<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngCmpnAboutCompText",
              "html": "<p>This section asks basic questions about your companion's age, breed, weight, and demeanor. The answers are required to complete the survey. If you don't know exact information, it's OK to guesstimate. If you can't answer the questions at all, it's probably best to abort the survey and try again at a later date when you know more about your companion's circumstances.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsAnimalType",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "radiogroup",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnAnimalType",
                      "title": "What kind of animal is {lndgRootCmpnName}?",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "choices": [
                        "Dog",
                        "Cat",
                        "Horse"
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsBreedGender",
                  "title": "What is {lndgRootCmpnName}'s breed or breed mix and gender?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnBreed",
                      "title": "Breed or mix (if unknown, type 'Don't know'):",
                      "isRequired": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnGender",
                      "title": "Gender:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Female",
                      "labelFalse": "Male"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsAge",
                  "title": "What is {lndgRootCmpnName}'s approximate age (in years and months)?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnAgeYears",
                      "title": "Age in years (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "min": "1",
                      "max": "40",
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 40,
                          "text": "Age must be between 1 and 40"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnAgeMonths",
                      "title": "Months (number 1 - 12)",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "min": 1,
                      "max": 12,
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 12,
                          "text": "Months must be between 1 and 12"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsWeight",
                  "title": "About how much does {lndgRootCmpnName} weigh in pounds or kilos?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnWeight",
                      "title": "Weight (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "min": 1,
                      "max": 2200,
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 2200,
                          "text": "Weight must be between 1 and 2200"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnWeightUnits",
                      "title": "Please choose pounds or kilos:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Kg",
                      "labelFalse": "Lbs"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsDemeanor",
                  "title": "How energetic, excitable, or anxious is {lndgRootCmpnName}? (1=very calm, 5=very excitable)?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "rating",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnDemeanor",
                      "title": ""
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngRootUserAnimalsPanel",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "dropdown",
                      "name": "lvngRootAnimalsCount",
                      "title": "How many animals do you have in your care?",
                      "required": true,
                      "choices": [
                        {
                          "value": "1",
                          "text": "Just {lndgRootCmpnName}"
                        },
                        {
                          "value": "2",
                          "text": "Two"
                        },
                        {
                          "value": "3",
                          "text": "Three"
                        },
                        {
                          "value": "4",
                          "text": "More than three"
                        }
                      ],
                      "choicesOrder": "none",
                      "otherText": "More than three",
                      "choicesMin": 1
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "lvngRootHasInsurance",
                      "required": true,
                      "title": "Do you have pet insurance for {lndgRootCmpnName}?"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "radiogroup",
                      "name": "lvngRootHasInsuranceOther",
                      "title": "Do you have pet insurance for your other animals?",
                      "visibleIf": "{lvngRootAnimalsCount} != 1",
                      "required": true,
                      "choices": [
                        {
                          "value": "1",
                          "text": "No"
                        },
                        {
                          "value": "2",
                          "text": "Some, but not all"
                        },
                        {
                          "value": "3",
                          "text": "All"
                        }
                      ],
                      "choicesOrder": "none"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lvngInfo_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngInfoPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngInfoHeading",
              "html": "<h3>How did you learn about laryngeal paralysis (LP)?</h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngCmpnAboutCompText",
              "html": "<p>This section asks some questions about how you learned about LP and whether the information you found helped you make decisions for {lndgRootCmpnName}. There is no right or wrong answer, so please answer as best as you can without thinking too hard about it.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngInfoInformedLevel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "boolean",
                  "name": "lvngInfoPriorInfo",
                  "title": "Had you ever heard of LP before {lndgRootCmpnName} got it?",
                  "isRequired": true
                },
                {
                  "type": "boolean",
                  "name": "lvngInfoLearningMore",
                  "title": "Now that you know about LP, have you been trying to learn more about it?",
                  "isRequired": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngInfoSourcesPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "checkbox",
                  "name": "lvngInfoSources",
                  "title": "Which sources of information have you accessed to learn about LP?",
                  "choices": [
                    {
                      "value": "Institutional websites",
                      "text": "Institutional websites (i.e. universities)"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "Private websites",
                      "text": "Private websites"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "Facebook groups",
                      "text": "Facebook groups"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "Primary veterinarians",
                      "text": "Primary veterinarians"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "Veterinary specialists",
                      "text": "Veterinary specialists (i.e. surgeons)"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "Social media video",
                      "text": "Youtube, Instagram or other video"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "Social media chat",
                      "text": "Reddit or other social media chat"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "AI models",
                      "text": "AI models like ChatGPT"
                    }
                  ],
                  "showOtherItem": true,
                  "showNoneItem": true,
                  "noneText": "Don't know",
                  "otherText": "Other (please describe)"
                },
                {
                  "type": "dropdown",
                  "name": "lvngInfoBestSource",
                  "title": "Which of those information sources did you find MOST useful (please select one)?",
                  "choices": [
                    "Facebook groups"
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngInfoQualityPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "rating",
                  "name": "lvngInfoHardToUnderstand",
                  "title": "Did you find the information you got about LP difficult to understand?",
                  "description": "1 = no, not difficult at all, 5 = very difficult",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "rateValues": [
                    {
                      "value": 1,
                      "text": "1"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 2,
                      "text": "2"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 3,
                      "text": "3"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 4,
                      "text": "4"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 5,
                      "text": "5"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "na",
                      "text": "Don't know"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "rating",
                  "name": "lvngInfoContradictory",
                  "title": "Do you feel like a lot of the information you got about LP was contradictory?",
                  "description": "1 = not at all contridictory, 5 = very contradictory",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "rateValues": [
                    {
                      "value": 1,
                      "text": "1"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 2,
                      "text": "2"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 3,
                      "text": "3"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 4,
                      "text": "4"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 5,
                      "text": "5"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "na",
                      "text": "Don't know"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "rating",
                  "name": "lvngInfoHardAnswers",
                  "title": "Did you find it hard to get clear answers to your questions so you could make informed choices for {lndgRootCmpnName}?",
                  "description": "1 = No, not hard at all, 5 = yes, very hard",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "rateValues": [
                    {
                      "value": 1,
                      "text": "1"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 2,
                      "text": "2"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 3,
                      "text": "3"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 4,
                      "text": "4"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": 5,
                      "text": "5"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "na",
                      "text": "Don't know"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "dcsdRoot_page",
      "visibleIf": "{lndgRootCrossedOver} = 'deceased'",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "dcsdRoot_panel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>Deceased Page</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdRootText",
              "html": "<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam. Sed nisi. Nulla quis sem at nibh elementum imperdiet. Duis sagittis ipsum.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdRootWhyContact",
              "html": "<img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='survey-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;<a href='https://example.com' class='survey-info-link' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Why provide a contact?</a>"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "dcsdRootUserContact",
              "title": "Facebook account name or email",
              "isRequired": true
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdCmpnAboutHeading",
              "html": "<h3>About your LP companion<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "dcsdCmpnAboutText",
              "html": "<p>We're focusing on dogs right now, but if you have a horse or cat with LP, feel free to answer the questions as best as you can. If a question doesn't apply, just leave it blank and skip to the next one.  </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "title": "Companion Details",
              "description": "Please share details about your LP companion here.",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsSubpanel1",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnName",
                      "title": "Name:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnBreed",
                      "title": "Breed or mix:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsSubpanel2",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnDOB",
                      "title": "Approximate date of birth:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "inputType": "date"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnGender",
                      "title": "Gender:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Female",
                      "labelFalse": "Male"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "dcsdCmpnDetailsSubpanel3",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnWeight",
                      "title": "Approximate weight (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "inputType": "number"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "dcsdCmpnWeightUnits",
                      "title": "Please choose pounds or kilos:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Kg",
                      "labelFalse": "Lbs"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}